> How can I set another model that using the lrtest I can get the Chi-square, df, and P value of factor A ?
> There is an example in the book (Mixed effects models and extensions in ecology with R), but I can't get the results in P284 (Like Year (X2 = 12.553, df = 2, p = 0.002), Area (X2 = 47.599, df = 3, p<  0.001))? .
> Can anyone help me? Thanks very much and best wishes!
> ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? Sincerely zhangshuang
